When trying to check if a CreateValidationResult is valid, it's possible for it to be invalid whilst still providing no helpful error messages. This makes debugging plugins which create issues a pain.

{code:title=Bar.java|borderStyle=solid}
if (createValidationResult.isValid())
 ........
else
 {
	System.out.println("Error!");

	for (String error : createValidationResult.getErrorCollection().getErrorMessages())
	{
		System.out.print(error);
	}
}

{code}

Tested in version 6.0.5, might occur in other versions.

